  "texts": [
    "The results may vary according to (1) the formulation of a prompt, (2) the timing of the prompt, and (3) the sequence of the prompt within a chat.",
    "Firstly, the formulation of a prompt varies depending on the type of task.",
    "In the case of this deductive research, there is a clear classification task and after settling on the most specific and sufficient prompt, the prompt can remain the same each time.",
    "However, since creating prompts is an iterative process, the researcher may decide to change the prompts depending on the research questions and the data.",
    "Secondly, LLMs are dynamic models so the output it provides may be different today than it was yesterday."
